estimateAmountOut(address,address,uint12.details: Estimates the amount out for a token swap using Uniswap V3.

params.tokenIn: The address of the input token.
params.tokenOut: The address of the output token.

returns.amountOut: The estimated amount of output token.

fulfillAssetsData(bytes32,address[],uint.details: Fulfills the asset data request from the Chainlink oracle.

getAmountOut(address,address,uint256,uin.details: Gets the amount out for a token swap.

params.tokenIn: The address of the input token.
params.tokenOut: The address of the output token.

getPortfolioBalance().details: Gets the portfolio balance in WETH.

initialize(address,address,address,bytes.details: Initializes the contract with the given parameters.

params._chainlinkToken: The address of the Chainlink token.
params._externalJobId: The external job ID for Chainlink requests.
params._factoryV2: The address of the Uniswap V2 factory.
params._factoryV3: The address of the Uniswap V3 factory.
params._oracleAddress: The address of the Chainlink oracle.
params._quoter: The address of the Uniswap V3 quoter.
params._swapRouterV2: The address of the Uniswap V2 swap router.
params._swapRouterV3: The address of the Uniswap V3 swap router.
params._toUsdPriceFeed: The address of the USD price feed.
params._token: The address of the IndexToken contract.
params._weth: The address of the WETH token.

mockFillAssetsList(address[],uint256[],u.details: Mock function to fill the asset list for testing purposes.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

requestAssetsData().details: Requests asset data from the Chainlink oracle.

setFeeRate(uint8).details: Sets the fee rate. The new fee should be between 1 to 100 (0.01% - 1%).

params._feeReceiver: The address of the fee receiver.

setPriceFeed(address).details: Sets the price feed address of the native coin to USD from the Chainlink oracle.

params._toUsdPricefeed: The address of native coin to USD price feed.

setUrl(string,string).details: Sets the base URL and URL parameters.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.
